      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The high-revving internals are protected by recent preventive rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive Dr. VANOS overhaul. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to handle the torque output of the M-Variable differential lock. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the vehicle retains its factory-spec suspension geometry and staggered Style 67 forged alloys. A true turn-key collector piece with a rigorous maintenance pedigree.",
